208
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] A sad to kaže Izrael isto.

209
00:40:31,119 --> 00:40:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da svi kažu nije.

210
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:44,000
